Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is consumed with sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, there is an untold story of the \Nbrothers Luffy and Ace from 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To The Sea Someday! The \NPledge of the Three Brats!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get stronger and I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's always a close \Nmatch between Ace and Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo! You gotta fight me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you run?! I have no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gum" again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just stretching your fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How interesting is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I keep saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is there any point in having that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! It's not working! It was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The rule is only 100 \Nmatches per person a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy lost 50 times to me and Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me vs. Ace is 24 - 26.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost by 2. Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! When I become 10 years \Nold, I'll beat you two up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be 13 then. Let's go \Nget something for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go for crocodiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love crocodile meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, don't get eaten this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were okay the last time \Nbecause you were swallowed whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here, Luffy. You can't \Nswim so you'd slow us dow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--I said "wait"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The harsh environment of Mt. Corvo \Nmade them stronger day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the north side of this mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is the place where all uncertain \Nthings end up called Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the north side of the Terminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a city with a solid stone \Nwall that doesn't let anyone enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only entrance to the city \Nis called the Great Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through which twice daily passes mountains \Nof junk from all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, here they come!\N--let's go treasure hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Residents of Gray Terminal visit the city \Nsometimes to sell recycled products.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait! What's in that package?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crocodile-skin. I'm here to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Great Gate, there is a boulevard \Nwhere all passersby can be clearly seen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then there is Edge Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Edge Town - where all the thugs and \Ngangsters from the city hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pops! Leave your package here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you say something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you mug somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be careful who you pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They are the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the walled city, \Nthere is another high stone wall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which encloses High Town where \Nroyalty and nobles live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this country is the Goa Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no garbage on streets
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it is said \Nto be the most beautiful country in the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windmill Village where Luffy was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the part of the kingdom even \Nthough it's a forgotten backwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.53,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DOWNTOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they paid so much for the skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got more for the "pirate savings"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer. We'll \Nhave great ramen noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is ramen? Is it really good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever's fine! I wanna eat soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,FINE DINING EIICHIRO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! People \Nlike you are not allowed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The VIP room will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That mark is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so honored to have a noble \Nlike you come to our restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll prepare a room right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is pretty handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I found it on the street a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are 3 ramen noodle bowls! \NThank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ramen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum-yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more. 3 more ramen noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we need to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn, they found out!\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch them, somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The ramen noodles were great!\N--I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Catch them?!\N--They're only kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's them again! They're such \Npests! Why were they let in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them run away! \NSomebody catch those 3 kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that they \Njumped out of the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 4th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost 26 bowls of ramen \Nnoodles and a window!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:13:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Manager! They left a note!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:08.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TREASURE TAB - LUFFY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Treasure tab"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be Sabo! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sabo! He's calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He confused me with someone else. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm not hiding anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are! Tell us, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have secrets among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tell us!\N--Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I'm not hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us, you bastard! Or I'll beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son of a noble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who is it?\N--Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And?\N--And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two asked me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, both of my parents are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not an orphan and I didn't \Ngrow up in the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who called to me today was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lying to you guys. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "sorry" so we gotta forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold off on forgiveness - \Nit all depends on your motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you living there if \Nyou are from a noble family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I ran away was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must acquire intelligence and \Nknowledge that you'll need as a noble
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a man that can marry \Na woman from the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we will live in security and \NI'm sure that you will live happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that if I could marry \Na royal woman, I'll live happily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cargo ship has sunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about the crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do about the \Ncargo that I paid for? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Clank. \N--Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a great loss! By thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.77,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DAD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! I drew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted from work, Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to draw this, \Nyou ought to be studying instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the royal family! \NWhich means I'm related to the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry me by piggyback to my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you rude jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you gonna ignore my royal order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just the son of some noble family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unforgivable to harm a \Nchild of the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo! Did you really have a fight \Nwith this royal boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he attacked me with \Na knife all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Did you get hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take him to a doctor \Nto get checked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we please settle this matter peacefully?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They love those who can maintain their \Nstatus and defend their property.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't marry a woman from \Nthe royal family, I'm worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they made me study \Nand take culture lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they were arguing everyday \Nbecause I wasn't doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no place to be in that family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:19:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for both of you but I was \Nall by myself even if I had parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you sneak out \Nand go somewhere sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you do but do you \Never go to the Gray Terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We nobles are privileged to live
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the High Town with \Nthe king and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those residents there and we nobles \Nare living in different worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you walk around a place like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you might get robbed and killed someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear the stories again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About countries across the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you guys have seen or visited!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're a strange kid!\N--Come and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobles have a low opinion \Nof the Gray Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's better than the stifling High Town
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where your life has been \Narranged for years to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta set out to sea someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of this \Ncountry and live freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the world out there \Nand write a book about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to study if it's about sailing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become stronger and \Nbecome pirates someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become one - you \Ndon't have to tell me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a pirate and \Ndefeat others and become infamous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the only proof of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if all the people \Nin the world reject me or despise me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a great pirate \Nand show them what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run from anybody or lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm feared or hated or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my name will be known all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! Alright then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool... I was wondering \Nwhat you'd have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see how you \Nturn out in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can all become pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it a problem that \Nwe all wanna become captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, I thought that you'd wanna \Nbe navigator on my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can come aboard my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No thanks!\N--No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come aboard! I said "come \Naboard", so you gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That will never happen!\N--Yeah, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're funny, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's just leave \Nit until the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll set out independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you stole that from Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can become brothers if we \Nexchange this cup of sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we become pirates, we \Nmight not be on the same ship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our brotherhood will always be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever, whatever, we'll \Nalways be bonded together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of the day when they'll \Ntake to the seas as pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his friends polish \Nup their bad-boy skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when an attack by a certain character \Nthreatens their peaceful lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the three boys are forced to say \Ngoodbye to the Dadan family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Leaving the Dadan Family for Good?! \NThe Kids' Hideout Has Been Built!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
